  "2026-06-09T15:56:05.593Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Subagent GitHub triage: no open PRs/issues/dependabot/security/code scanning/secret scanning/advisories; daily Auto Release and Release succeeded on 2026-06-09. Actionable external finding: Nightly Validation run 27192052551 failed on windows-latest Node 20 while loading tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts with SyntaxError; investigating before PR closeout."
  "2026-06-09T16:02:01.463Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Evidence: implemented timeout-bounded deactivateExtensions with a 5000ms default and typed ExtensionDeactivationOptions, SDK barrel export, docs, and regression coverage for a hanging project extension not blocking a healthy global teardown. Verification passed: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk-index.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage => 2606 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; pnpm typecheck; pnpm quality:static; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate; package doctor ok; pm health ok; manual isolated temp smoke passed."
  "2026-06-09T16:17:37.938Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review polish: CodeRabbit noted that timed-out deactivate promises continue in the background because JavaScript promises are not cancellable. Added an inline note in runExtensionDeactivateWithTimeout; focused extension-loader coverage rerun before push."
  "2026-06-09T16:24:22.513Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review follow-up: Gemini found that positive fractional deactivate_timeout_ms values below 1ms could floor to 0 and timeout immediately. Changed normalization to Math.max(1, Math.floor(...)) and added extension-loader regression coverage for 0.5ms normalizing to a 1ms timeout."
  "2026-06-09T16:31:04.039Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review follow-up: Gemini flagged setTimeout overflow for extremely large deactivate_timeout_ms values. Added MAX_EXTENSION_DEACTIVATE_TIMEOUT_MS=2147483647 and cap normalized positive values after flooring/clamping to at least 1ms."
  "2026-06-09T16:38:31.852Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review follow-up: Gemini suggested explicit no-timeout handling for host-provided 0/Infinity and documenting the opt-out. Added normalization support, bypassed Promise.race for timeoutMs=0, documented SDK behavior, and added extension-loader tests for 0 and Infinity."
